I am really happy right now! I got it to work!!!
Here is what I did to be able to watch the film at 99,9% completion:
-Opened cz-fishbone.part001 in winrar and started extracting (dont mind the missing part message in the beginnining)
-When the extraction was at 99%, I pressed pause and went to task manager. in task manager i removed the winrar process (I dont get the error message then (and the rar file is not deleted afterwards)
-The bieffects is just that you lose a few seconds of the ending text (which doesn't matter anyways now does it? :P)
Good luck all of you that is stuck at 99,9%

Good for you cybro, dont work for me.
How do you abort the process in task manger?

To abort the process in Task Manager:

You press Ctrl + Alt + Delete that bring upp the Task Manager... Under Applications mark the program you whant to end then press End Task bottom... Woola.... :)
